{
  "stem": "17543.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 117.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I got to the bottom of this C-lager called where we was in, I recognized there is like-- I can't compare it to anything.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's just full length of a-- a barrack was empty.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But in the-- on the floor is some wooden or, or, or stone long like low tables and holes in it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we, people was sitting back to back on that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was toilet.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I didn't know what it is.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we wasn't eating so long ago, drinking when we needed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Why these people was there I have no idea.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But that was the very last, it was the end of the C-lager, that's a row of two side at that street of barracks.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I went in there, huge number of people was sitting, I think with two rows of back to back, you know.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "People were sitting on that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I was shouting top of my voice, Mommy, Mommy, Mrs.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Hochhauser.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And all of the suddenly, I recognized [SOBBING] I was standing front of my mother.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But I didn't recognized her, because we went in in normal clothes and hair.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And there was no hair and just a rag.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we just broke down and cried, because she didn't recognize me either.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Just recognized what I was shouting for.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I was only 12.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Now, I was [? 13 ?] in January.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And that was sometime in March or April.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I don't know when, but was not very long after.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It was really terrible, so I never went back to that barrack where I was supposed to go I went to the barrack where she said she supposed to go to.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So in-between these barracks had a, a place where was-- people could drink water, called washroom.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
